### List recipes
GET http://localhost:8787/recipes

### Scale recipe
POST http://localhost:8787/scale-recipe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipeId": "banana-bread",
  "targetServings": 12
}

### Shopping list from two recipes
POST http://localhost:8787/shopping-list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipeIds": ["banana-bread", "choc-chip-cookies"]
}

### Substitution suggestions
POST http://localhost:8787/substitute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredient": "egg"
}

### Plan meal (summary + shopping list)
POST http://localhost:8787/plan-meal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipes": [
    { "recipeId": "perfect-cc-cookies", "servings": 16 },
    { "recipeId": "banana-bread", "servings": 8 }
  ]
}

### Transform recipe (diet profile + sugar cap)
POST http://localhost:8787/recipe/perfect-cc-cookies/transform
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dietaryProfile": "dairy-free",
  "maxSugarCup": 0.75,
  "servings": 12
}

### Pantry match
POST http://localhost:8787/pantry-match
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pantryItems": ["flour", "egg", "butter", "sugar", "banana"],
  "limit": 3
}

### Leftovers remix
POST http://localhost:8787/leftovers-remix
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leftovers": ["rice", "chicken"],
  "pantry": ["egg", "soy sauce", "green onion"]
}

### Batch prep plan
POST http://localhost:8787/batch-prep
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "days": 4,
  "recipes": [
    { "recipeId": "perfect-cc-cookies", "servings": 16 },
    { "recipeId": "banana-bread", "servings": 8 }
  ]
}
